Symbol.Script_3D:
! ================================================================ ! Detail Level ! ================================================================
if gs_detlevel_3D_m=0 then END if GLOB_CONTEXT>20 and GLOB_CONTEXT<40 then gs_detlevel_3D_m=1
if gs_detlevel_3D_m=1 then RESOL 4 if gs_detlevel_3D_m=2 then RESOL gs_resol
! ================================================================ ! 3D Hotspots ! ================================================================ addz placementHeight
unID=1
hotspot 0,0,0, unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot a,0,0, unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,b,0, unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot a,b,0, unID : unID=unID+1
hotspot a, b, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, b, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, b, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0, b, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, b, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, b, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot a, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, 0, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
if gs_door_bw = 0 then ! asymmetric door widths are enabled if gs_full_edit=1 then ! Door Panel Streching if gs_door_type_m > 0 then hotspot left_cab+0, front_cab,toe_h+door_h,unID,door_w,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot left_cab-1, front_cab,toe_h+door_h,unID,door_w,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot left_cab+door_w, front_cab,toe_h+door_h,unID,door_w,2 : unID=unID+1 endif endif endif del 1
! ================================================================ !Base Babinet ! ================================================================
addz placementHeight pen gs_cont_pen material gs_cabinet_mat if not(gs_shadow) then SHADOW OFF
! ----- Simple Geometry ------------------------------------------- ! -----------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_detlevel_3D_m=1 then addy fr_th1 mulID = 0 if right_panel and left_panel then addx 0.02 : mulID = mulID + 1 endif if not(right_panel) and left_panel then addx 0.02 : mulID = mulID + 1 endif
PRISM_ 5,zzyzx, 0, 0, 15, a - (left_panel* 0.02) - (right_panel * 0.02), 0, 15, a - (left_panel* 0.02) - (right_panel * 0.02), b - fr_th1 - (dob_face * fr_th1), 15, 0, b - fr_th1 - (dob_face * fr_th1), 15, 0, 0, -1 del 1 if mulID > 0 then del mulID endif else ! ----- Detailed Geometry ----------------------------------------- ! ----------------------------------------------------------------- CALL "fa_gen_basecabinet" PARAMETERS a=a, b=b, zzyzx=zzyzx, gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m, dob_face=dob_face, count_th=0, front_cab=0, rear_cab=rear_cab, left_cab=left_cab,fr_th1=fr_th1, right_cab=right_cab, toe_h=0, side_vis_m=0, sink=0, shelf_num=shelf_num, gs_ShelfMat=gs_ShelfMat, gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, gs_shadow=gs_shadow, toe_mat=0, gs_cabinet_mat=gs_cabinet_mat, drawer=0, ToeHtps3D=0, basecab_unID=unID, returned_parameters unID endif
! ================================================================ ! Door Panels ! ================================================================
for ii=1 to (dob_face)+1 !*** double face ADD left_cab,front_cab+fr_th1,toe_h if gs_door_type_m > 0 and (abs(door_w)>EPS)then GOSUB "FrontDoorLeft" ! in case door_w = 0 ,the left door won't be called. Result: single-door cabinet ADDx a-right_cab-left_cab mulx -1 if gs_door_type_m > 0 and (abs(door_w - (a-right_cab-left_cab))>EPS) then GOSUB "FrontDoorRight" ! in case door_w = A (the left door is as wide as the object itself) ,the right door won't be called. Result: single-door cabinet del 1 del 2
ADDY front_cab ROTZ 180 ADD -A+right_cab-left_cab,-B+rear_cab,0 next ii del (dob_face+1)*3
! ================================================================ ! End Panels ! ================================================================ if rear_panel=1 then door_w=a-door_w-left_cab-right_cab door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th ADD door_w+left_cab,b-rear_cab,toe_h ROTZ 180 GOSUB "EndPanels" door_w=a-door_w-left_cab-right_cab ADDX -door_w GOSUB "EndPanels" del 3 endif
if left_panel=1 then door_w=b-fr_th1-rear_cab-(fr_th1*dob_face): door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th !*** LEFT END PANEL ADD left_cab,door_w+fr_th1,toe_h ROTZ -90 GOSUB "EndPanels" del 2 endif
if right_panel=1 then door_w=b-fr_th1-rear_cab-(fr_th1*dob_face): door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th ADD a-right_cab,fr_th1,toe_h ROTZ 90 GOSUB "EndPanels" del 2 endif
del 1
! ================================================================ END ! END ! END ! END ! END ! END ! END ! END ! END ! ! ================================================================
! ----------------------------------------------------------------- "FrontDoorLeft": ! -----------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_door_bw=0 then door_w=door_w else door_w=(a-left_cab-right_cab)/2 endif
cabdoortyp_unID=unID CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_full_edit=gs_full_edit,door_ang=door_ang,door_w=door_w,door_h=door_h, gs_door_type_m=gs_door_type_m,gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p,doorframe_w=doorframe_w, vert_gnum=vert_gnum,hor_gnum=hor_gnum,gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, gs_shadow=gs_shadow,doorglas_mat=doorglas_mat,doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat, fr_th1=fr_th1,gs_bevel=gs_bevel, gs_knob_type_m=gs_knob_type_m,gs_knob_p_m=gs_knob_p_m,knob_size=knob_size, knob_pl_x=knob_pl_x,knob_pl_y=knob_pl_y, gs_knob_mat=gs_knob_mat, cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID, gs_cust_knob = gs_cust_knob, gs_customHandleLength = gs_customHandleLength, gs_customHandleHeight = gs_customHandleHeight, gs_customHandleDepth = gs_customHandleDepth, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
unID = cabdoortyp_unID return
! ----------------------------------------------------------------- "FrontDoorRight": ! -----------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_door_bw=1 then door_w=(a-left_cab-right_cab)/2 else door_w=a-door_w-left_cab-right_cab endif
cabdoortyp_unID=unID CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_full_edit=gs_full_edit,door_ang=door_ang,door_w=door_w,door_h=door_h, gs_door_type_m=gs_door_type_m,gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p,doorframe_w=doorframe_w, vert_gnum=vert_gnum,hor_gnum=hor_gnum,gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, gs_shadow=gs_shadow,doorglas_mat=doorglas_mat,doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat, fr_th1=fr_th1,gs_bevel=gs_bevel, gs_knob_type_m=gs_knob_type_m,gs_knob_p_m=gs_knob_p_m,knob_size=knob_size, knob_pl_x=knob_pl_x,knob_pl_y=knob_pl_y, gs_knob_mat=gs_knob_mat, cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID, gs_cust_knob = gs_cust_knob, gs_customHandleLength = gs_customHandleLength, gs_customHandleHeight = gs_customHandleHeight, gs_customHandleDepth = gs_customHandleDepth, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
unID = cabdoortyp_unID return
! ----------------------------------------------------------------- "EndPanels": ! -----------------------------------------------------------------
! on rear panel there is no glas and grilles and knobs!! door_ang=0 gs_knob_type_m=0 If iEndPanelType = 1 then gs_door_type_m=1 If iEndPanelType = 2 then gs_door_type_m=2 If iEndPanelType = 4 then gs_door_type_m=11 If iEndPanelType = 7 then gs_door_type_m=4 If iEndPanelType = 9 then gs_door_type_m=6 If iEndPanelType = 99 then gs_door_type_m=10 gs_full_edit=0
cabdoortyp_unID=unID CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS ALL cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID, fr_th1=0.02,gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p_end,doorframe_w=doorframe_w_end, doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat_end,doorglas_mat=doorframe_mat_end, gs_bevel=gs_bevel, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
unID = cabdoortyp_unID return
Symbol.Script_2D:
pen gs_cont_pen line_type gs_line_type ADD2 a/2,b/2
unID=1 hotspot2 -a/2,b/2, unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0,b/2, unID : unID=unID+1
n = side_vis2D_m mod 2 m = int(side_vis2D_m / 2 + EPS) mod 2
! Fill of Cabinet FILL gs_fill_type POLY2_B 5, 1+2+64,gs_fill_pen,gs_back_pen, -a/2,-b/2,n, -a/2,b/2,1, a/2,b/2,m, a/2,-b/2,1, -a/2,-b/2,-1
hotline2 -a/2,-b/2,-a/2,b/2 hotline2 -a/2,b/2,a/2,b/2 hotline2 a/2,b/2,a/2,-b/2 hotline2 a/2,-b/2,-a/2,-b/2
del 1 CALL "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" Parameters ALL
If iCabSymbolType2D <> 1 then
if iCabSymbolType2D = 2 OR iCabSymbolType2D = 4 then line2 0,0.025,a,0.025 line2 a/2,0,a/2,0.025 endif if iCabSymbolType2D = 3 OR iCabSymbolType2D = 4 then line2 0,0,cos(15)*a/2,-sin(15)*a/2 line2 a,0,a-(cos(15)*a/2),-sin(15)*a/2 arc2 0,0,a/2,-15,0 arc2 a,0,a/2,180,195 endif
If dob_face = 1 then add2 0,b+Front_cab+rear_cab mul2 1,-1
if iCabSymbolType2D = 2 OR iCabSymbolType2D = 4 then line2 0,0.025,a,0.025 line2 a/2,0,a/2,0.025 endif if iCabSymbolType2D = 3 OR iCabSymbolType2D = 4 then line2 0,0,cos(15)*a/2,-sin(15)*a/2 line2 a,0,a-(cos(15)*a/2),-sin(15)*a/2 arc2 0,0,a/2,-15,0 arc2 a,0,a/2,180,195 endif
del 2 endif endif
